‚öîÔ∏è Simulation Constraints & Assumptions
	‚Ä¢	No nuclear, chemical, or biological weapons at any time.
	‚Ä¢	Conventional warfare only, including land, sea, air, space, cyber, and electronic domains.
	‚Ä¢	Each coalition operates under a unified command structure (e.g., Supreme Allied Command vs. Supreme Axis Command).
